{"title":"照亮中国","authors":["商泽军"],"dates":[{"year":2002,"month":11,"day":9}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"照亮中国"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"商泽军"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九二一年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一种金属被锻造成"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"镰刀和锤头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在中国南方的一处城市"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"砸响"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这种金属的刚性"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来自古老东方的地层"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"然后和西方淬火"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火星四溅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把黑的穹幕烧穿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锤头是开拓的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"镰刀是收获的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而火星是虔诚的播种"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从水乡的漠漠田野"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到北国的黄土畦垄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从人的内心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到交流的话语"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从河流的水声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到山的轰鸣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都有这播种的身影"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它在暗夜中播种曙光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在痛苦中播种反抗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它用锤子进行攒击"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"血的火的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一切的一切历经一遍"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它成熟了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是怎样的成熟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"布满着血痂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伤痕累累又青春的眉眼和激情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是时候了 镰刀开始收获"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就像庄稼成熟了收割一样"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它收割了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"收获一九四九年十月的锣鼓"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和播种时期待的心情"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}